{"tid":1336313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁朝偉加盟Marvel做反派 於《上氣》出演「滿大人」","createTime":"2019-07-21T01:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T03:10:06.000Z","uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"007f79bd4e8e3ba9ae36bee5df0409f28810cee6","tid":1336313,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T01:59:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59845954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59845954&d=3A6Iqvk0VBPdaidkhJ82W%2FzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=b14074f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D59845954&h=85d266e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=59845954</a>"},{"pid":"80309ed1019446bf51f53d010613411476275488","tid":1336313,"uid":23707,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:00:16.000Z","msg":"Marvel在《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers：Endgame）後，已積極籌備新階段之電影，當中更有首部華裔英雄電影《上氣》（Shang-Chi），今天在聖地牙哥動漫節中，Marvel便公佈了有關《上氣》的消息。<br />\n<br />\n今天公佈了《上氣》的戲名為《上氣：The Legend of the Ten Rings》，見到「Ten Rings」便會想到在《鋼鐵奇俠3》中的恐怖組織，當時滿大人更是受到fans期待，但可惜在《鋼鐵奇俠3》中的滿大人只是一個演員，不是真正的恐怖份子，而今天Marvel便公佈了《上氣》會有「真滿大人」現身，更由梁朝偉出演，令fans大為期待。<br />\n<br />\n其實在去年，偉仔接受大陸一間雜誌訪問，當中他已透露自己最想做反派，這次真的得嘗所願。"},{"pid":"bbf09bdb23b9b36fccec1b1c5d57449ace3c402b","tid":1336313,"uid":59114,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:02:19.000Z","msg":"ok我會入場睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾撚驚會搵d大陸演員嚟拍,吳京個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ffd458174ab0e45354004e3b58a21b616b6a293","tid":1336313,"uid":35508,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T02:02:57.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" cla